  <examples>
    <example name="Additive record-extension on `AnalysisChunk` (reference: design.md Â§4.3)" location="projects/spaarke-ai-platform-unification-r5/design.md">
      design.md Â§4.3 (lines ~297â€“315) shows the target shape:
      ```
      record AnalysisChunk(
        string Type,        // existing + NEW: "delta"
        string? Content,
        bool Done,
        string? Summary,
        DocumentAnalysisResult? Result,
        string? Error,
        FieldDelta? Delta); // NEW (nullable)

      record FieldDelta(
        string Path,        // JSON path, e.g., "tldr", "fileHighlights[0].summary"
        string Content,     // token chunk for this field
        int Sequence);      // for ordering correctness
      ```
      Adapt to match the actual current `AnalysisChunk.cs` shape (positional record with
      `[property: JsonPropertyName(...)]` attributes â€” see &lt;knowledge&gt; pattern 1).
    </example>
    <example name="Wizard consumer discriminant filter (back-compat reference)" location="src/solutions/LegalWorkspace/src/components/SummarizeFiles/summarizeService.ts">
